  <prompt>
    Build the EventFormController PCF control's Event Type fetching functionality. The control
    fetches the selected Event Type's configuration (required fields, hidden fields) and makes
    it available for form field visibility management.
  </prompt>

  <role>
    SPAARKE platform developer with expertise in PCF control development and Dataverse form integration.
    Follow ADR-022 for React 16 APIs. Follow ADR-021 for Fluent UI v9.
  </role>

  <goal>
    EventFormController fetches Event Type configuration when bound to Event Type field. The
    configuration data is parsed and ready for field visibility logic in subsequent task.
  </goal>

  <context>
